{"tid":908624,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"無希望就唔會有失望","createTime":"2018-11-19T16:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T16:38:48.000Z","uid":204618,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2cf2c20818574ce736f798d923cefcc3cecd4414","tid":908624,"uid":204618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T16:37:32.000Z","msg":"永遠唔會奢望人地對我好<br />\n永遠覺得人地要求我做咩 我都應該做<br />\n就算有希望都會用盡所有籍口<br />\n同自己講唔應該有希望 <br />\n唔係一個人 係對所有事情都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好撚厭世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求知音人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27af229fe3eee5845a8a301ee8eea59393813e0","tid":908624,"uid":21355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T16:40:17.000Z","msg":"慣了就好 乜都求其啦"},{"pid":"62104d1c26459e2e9abe8d0802f0e9b085f8bd95","tid":908624,"uid":133042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T16:42:07.000Z","msg":"我明, 已經麻木咗, 對咩都無乜感覺"},{"pid":"b905e33e453f595c212d64affbaf64952a76eac3","tid":908624,"uid":222033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T16:44:38.000Z","msg":"過得一日得一日啦<br />\n都係等死嗰日嚟啫"},{"pid":"3fb323bc303ce4b4f43b084f1f53c76c974e43e6","tid":908624,"uid":130090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T16:45:26.000Z","msg":"變左淨係識聽人講既木偶"},{"pid":"acf1e94ff2869d6cb0b5494c64007a730938c313","tid":908624,"uid":58880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T16:48:22.000Z","msg":"樣衰都麻木左求安樂死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb96e4f4bc76245b2ba8df44058640741836d150","tid":908624,"uid":119401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T17:18:10.000Z","msg":"係咩"},{"pid":"08b71f31e7abc24045d051d8f4ad9e5b47566400","tid":908624,"uid":204618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T17:20:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過得一日得一日啦<br />\n都係等死嗰日嚟啫</blockquote><br />\n係 覺得死一啲都唔可怕 而係解脱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9cb6aef8c2f07605ece4b9efa10dff5425bdcf2","tid":908624,"uid":78595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T18:49:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bcb8d56bcd66eab7d704d0e6e521ad4729740943","tid":908624,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T18:51:04.000Z","msg":"不渴望"},{"pid":"ad60973196355757de750e0bf03336e709e9515d","tid":908624,"uid":152047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T19:29:08.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<br />\n我永遠隨傳隨到、有求必應<br />\n只係希望喺人心中佔少少地位、多少都好<br />\n但換黎嘅係一次又一次嘅忽視、可有可無咁<br />\n永遠只有危急關頭下先會被記起"},{"pid":"ccc16054a0b4c3ab0ec0002900285fc5a07814bc","tid":908624,"uid":182430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T19:29:56.000Z","msg":"係奢望"},{"pid":"246ae2d4adad81db3a5199a256ce3ba87bf16363","tid":908624,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T09:12:45.000Z","msg":"相信你心中一定非常痛苦，才會如此寫下你的心聲！雖然，我並未完全了解你，但我明白置身痛苦中是怎樣一回事。有些人在困苦之中，會選擇放棄自己，不知道你是否也有這自殺的念頭？<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n無論你是否想過放棄自己，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡。因為人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=Kw%2FU6yUwWLd772NRwAvJUZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=c709b872\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"343d0fcf9b9359cbe3d167d9457b87b72ad7c734","tid":908624,"uid":204618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T09:19:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同你一樣<br />\n我永遠隨傳隨到、有求必應<br />\n只係希望喺人心中佔少少地位、多少都好<br />\n但換黎嘅係一次又一次嘅忽視、可有可無咁<br />\n永遠只有危急關頭下先會被記起</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一諗有啲朋友係咁就好頹"},{"pid":"972f89962f39ce014c16b11cc9a0afd24fadb6ed","tid":908624,"uid":62904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T10:17:51.000Z","msg":"上次咁講 比人話好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時對所有野都抱希望個傷害仲大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  屌1999"},{"pid":"0c049bc477bfed591c483c49df19ff91a7a4c43d","tid":908624,"uid":107219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T10:26:57.000Z","msg":"其實做地底泥幾好，因為已經最底，冇野可以失去，個人冇咁大壓力，自在啲，但求活得一日得一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8fa9f3b7a6a12dc2431759a66463984b2987358","tid":908624,"uid":204618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T16:33:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實做地底泥幾好，因為已經最底，冇野可以失去，個人冇咁大壓力，自在啲，但求活得一日得一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇完好想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a404a6e11d5bb39576586f3bdbc1bf91ec5a651","tid":908624,"uid":204618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T16:36:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次咁講 比人話好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時對所有野都抱希望個傷害仲大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  屌1999</blockquote><br />\n永遠講呢句 其實係因為永遠抱太多希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過現實係殘酷<img src=\